Roadmap
-------

0.0.6
-----

- Remove transaction from account, (by ID)

0.0.7
-----

- Add a transaction to an account, given another account, desc, date, etc.

0.1.0
-----

- Save an opened GnuCash file back so that it matches what was read (a
  bit for bit match)

- Function for adding a transaction

- Function for removing a transaction (by ID)

0.2.0
-----

- Function for adding an account

- Function for removing an account (by ID)

0.3.0
-----

- Functions for getting any template transactions that should be applied

- Functions for adding transactions by template

0.4.0
-----

- ???
